data.title: Google Android 17 leaks: Cinnamon Bun codename, new UI and smarter AI features tipped | Mint
data.description: Google is reportedly gearing up for Android 17, expected to launch a stable build by June 2026. Codenamed Cinnamon Bun, the update may bring a refreshed Material 3 UI, improved privacy, enhanced desktop mode, and smarter AI-driven features.
data.author: Govind Choudhary
